# ✨ Quote Generator

A simple web app that fetches and displays a random inspirational quote using the Quotable API.

## 🚀 Features

- Fetches a new quote on button click
- Displays quote and author
- Author name is shown in bold
- Clean and simple layout

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript (ES6)
- Axios for HTTP requests
- [Quotable API](https://api.quotable.io)

## 📦 Setup Instructions

1. Clone or download this repository.
2. Open `index.html` in your browser.
3. Click the **"Generate Quote"** button to fetch a new quote.

## 🔍 API Used-

**Endpoint**: `https://api.quotable.io/random`  
**Sample Response**:

```json
{
  "content": "Be yourself; everyone else is already taken.",
  "author": "Oscar Wilde"
}
```
